      "span_text": "Previously, patients have been instructed that they should have a responsible person available to escort them from their procedure and be available to help with their care for 24 hours after their procedure. [CITATION_1] With proper preparation, the use of more short-acting anesthetic/sedation medications, and sound clinical judgment, this axiom may no longer be true.",
